      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p>A plain <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">masonry block</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.235</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.40</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.56</measure>), on the face of which a <rs type="decoration">tabella
ansata</rs> has been incised. The face is fairly worn.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p>The date, a, is written above the <term lang="la">tabella</term> and
down the right side, which is worn; the main text, b, is
written within the <term lang="la">tabella</term>, with each line of verse separated
by an incised line.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p>Av. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.02</measure>;
irregular.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="date">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p><date value="0543" notBefore="0543" notAfter="0543" exact="both">A.D. 543</date> or <date value="0558" notBefore="0558" notAfter="0558" exact="both">A.D. 558</date> (<rs type="criteria">indiction</rs>, <rs type="criteria">emperor</rs>).</p>
      </div>

